  README.md:706:| `ConsulConfigPreprocessor`      | Replaces strings of the form consul://key by looking up the value of 'key' from a [Consul](https://www.consul.io/) server.<br/><br/>This preprocessor requires the `hoplite-consul` module to be added to the classpath.                                                                                               |
